<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA51">
<l>maṉavāḷu mōraivar vaṉkuṟumpar tammai</l>
<l>ciṉamāḷvit tōriṭattē cērttu puṉamēya</l>
<l>taṇṭuḻā yāṉaṭiyē tāṉkāṇum aḵtaṉṟē</l>
<l>vaṇṭuḻāñ cīrākku māṇpu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having mastered the anger of those who are strongly fortified,</l>
<l>the once Five that master the mind, [and] joined them in one place,</l>
<l>seeing the feet of him with cool Tulsi from the fields, isn’t it,</l>
<l>is the honour that creates the excellence that stirs liberally.(?)</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
